Name: postmarkup
Version: 1.1.4
Summary: BBCode to (X)HTML rendering engine
Home-page: http://code.google.com/p/postmarkup/
Author: Will McGugan
Author-email: will@willmcgugan.com
License: Python Software Foundation License
Download-URL: http://code.google.com/p/postmarkup/downloads/list
Description: Converts BBCode (http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/BBCode) in to HTML and
        XHTML snippets. Always outputs valid XHTML, even from badly nested BBCode.
        
